venice.lib.networkRSB

Class NamedPairList

  • java.lang.Object
    • venice.lib.networkRSB.NamedPairList

  • public class NamedPairList
extends java.lang.Object
    Maintains a list of named pairs for the class matcher. Everything is still abstract (means: only strings, no real classes or methods).
